:44.000Z","msg":"f3果年日日帶左一年day con<br />\n<br />\n第二年對眼已經開始易乾 就冇再日日搞 出街同有重要嘢先帶<br />\n<br />\n而家眼都係易乾果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要眼藥水跟身 所以出街都戴眼鏡多 見重要人/有重要事要好睇啲嘅時候先戴con"},{"pid":"4846aa9e5903f84b58fb3f4fe77e4deb05a01173","tid":901294,"uid":215448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d9a4ddbb72aa25910d4e700928b0554d659986","tid":901294,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d934c27665f2aeda9c0a967cefd0e41d265eba00","tid":901294,"uid":215448,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:37:36.000Z","msg":"持續日日帶 帶左十年 有一排開始痛 而家淨係出街先帶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"人地話戴左十年con唔可以再戴 <br />\n會有問題 <br />\n你去做嬌視激光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"係 我都聽過<br />\n所以我覺得好準 真係到差唔多十年就痛<br />\n過去呢10年幾乎冇出過事發過炎之類<br />\n但我冇打算做激光<br />\n而家1個月都係帶3-5日<br />\n就冇再痛了<br />\n盡量少帶好"},{"pid":"85bea623147dcee86606c317560139d3cdae3e23","tid":901294,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d520dbd07a2af4417210bd81226cc64eeaa1f954","tid":901294,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da04b10954f94ced1dd07bc43e8be8b585ef8428","tid":901294,"uid":100550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打係近視越黎越淺 <br />\n或者淺左少少？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"我好似淺咗少少<br />\n似乎因為老花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:39:24.000Z","msg":"我遠視<br />\n以前去check佢話遠視會退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚佢會退，我靠副眼鏡放大左隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405a23dd49f55bf6f10d0580abfded326876337e","tid":901294,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4846aa9e5903f84b58fb3f4fe77e4deb05a01173","tid":901294,"uid":215448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s