.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過一早上機 去到玩到半夜對眼乾到就黎甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e69351b37a831cae38227ee023d3cc580a3150","tid":901294,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:27:23.000Z","msg":"可以試下acuvue oasys day con<br />\n真係好戴到好似無戴一樣<br />\n戴左一年到so far 都無咩唔舒服<br />\n雖然幾貴但值得<br />\n利申 單邊近視200度 戴con淨係戴一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無戴果邊反而乾過有戴果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03159e45158de12ef5d1467bc45b7d02a068fb2","tid":901294,"uid":173162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"買定眼藥水，一枝用完即棄果隻"},{"pid":"919aa4f4c50594267f1052668c6456248ac40c14","tid":901294,"uid":93062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"贈你四字,矽水凝膠"},{"pid":"c8a767d8b7a0c6cdb74b1dfb4011c1645fa3d7ff","tid":901294,"uid":17388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"平時返屋企就唔帶"},{"pid":"289a462ade5ee8274c13a0440d11c63b0fa54dfa","tid":901294,"uid":189178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"其實話con齡得十幾年個啲好似係以前既事<br />\n而家整con技術好左好似話唔會再咁焗住對眼 所以戴成世都冇問題<br />\n利申：聽翻黎 冇考究過<br />\n不過我而家都日日戴con返工，feel到對眼視力差左....乾就冇咩"},{"pid":"63c6da5dcb5fc0090c8646f6d85a5eb784931009","tid":901294,"uid":215448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"405a23dd49f55bf6f10d0580abfded326876337e","tid":901294,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4846aa9e5903f84b58fb3f4fe77e4deb05a01173","tid":901294,"uid":215448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d9a4ddbb72aa25910d4e700928b0554d659986","tid":901294,"uid":221589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"人地話戴左十年con唔可以再戴 <br />\n會有問題 <br />\n你去做嬌視激光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T05:38:35.000Z","msg":"係 我都聽過<br />\n所以